{"tid":2229212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網媒PPPN創辦人被指串謀傷人獲釋候查 被指涉「屠龍小隊」案件","createTime":"2020-10-04T08:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T21:29:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8451d902bb688a84f6cdd41042d148dc3dae10","tid":2229212,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"曾代表民主派參選立法會飲食界的網媒「PPPN International」創辦人伍永德，據報在本月1日被警方以「串謀有意圖傷人」罪拘捕，案件更由警方國安全處跟進。伍現時已獲釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n網媒「PPPN international」日前在Facebook專頁公佈，創辦人伍永德早前被捕，律師指罪名為「串謀傷人」，他其後獲釋候查。《蘋果》曾向「PPPN international」及伍查詢詳情，暫未獲回覆。北京喉舌《文匯報》今日引述消息指，伍懷疑涉與「屠龍小隊」案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆指，國安處人員經深入調查後，於10月1日在灣仔區拘捕1名34歲姓伍本地男子，涉嫌與一宗在去年12月發生的「串謀有意圖傷人」案有關。該名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於11月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n伍永德於14年傘運後，曾以「傘兵」身份在16年立法會選舉中在飲食界功能組別挑戰張宇人，惜最終落敗。去年反送中運動其間，他亦向警方申請去年8月2日的旺角大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/QIDAKWRB7FBFRBHZGWPJJROTWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FQIDAKWRB7FBFRBHZGWPJJROTWU%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c88cfe61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FQIDAKWRB7FBFRBHZGWPJJROTWU%2F&h=a51a048a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/QIDAKWRB7FBFRBHZGWPJJROTWU/</a>"},{"pid":"b1db1d2f80b46bce07ada3338539966c5ce99aea","tid":2229212,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98529441bd48f1b491be636c434766fb57f7320c","tid":2229212,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1db1d2f80b46bce07ada3338539966c5ce99aea","tid":2229212,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"